 (I've re-added a cc so that we can make sure we get the bug report
 taken care of)
 
 How did you get it to happen the first time? 
 
 To find the preferences file, evaluate:
 
   (find-system-path 'pref-file)
 
 you should only need to delete the line containing:
 
   drscheme:language-settings
 
 Thanks,
 Robby
 
